gantt
    title Distributed Trace - Order Request
    dateFormat X
    axisFormat %L ms

    section API Gateway
    Parse & Route           :0, 5

    section Order Service
    Validate Order          :5, 15
    Check Inventory (gRPC)  :15, 45

    section Inventory Service
    Query Database          :20, 40

    section Order Service
    Process Payment         :45, 80

    section Payment Service
    Charge Card (External)  :50, 75

    section Order Service
    Save Order              :80, 95
    Send Response           :95, 100
